{"tid":656970,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《復仇者聯盟3》 拍一天燒近350萬 預算幾億美元仍不夠","createTime":"2018-05-07T16:46:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T07:20:03.000Z","uid":66943,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"89839dcaf7f30de252a2573c8c9c84741b0992ab","tid":656970,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T16:46:57.000Z","msg":"據媒體Comicbookmovie報導，導演羅素兄弟透露，《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》平均每天的生產成本超過45萬美元（約合350萬港幣）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://theterrorofknowing.files.wordpress.com/2018/04/infinitywar.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheterrorofknowing.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F04%2Finfinitywar.jpg&h=30becbdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bm1Vy-e2uy8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBm1Vy-e2uy8&d=Pj%2BB3uaseRIJ2Z2MBWY%2FHQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=76e665b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bm1Vy-e2uy8</a><br />\n<br />\n　Joseph Russo表示：&ldquo;Marvel的電影已經有18部，通常在電影成功後，演員的片酬都會上漲。此外，這類電影中，視覺特效需要耗費大量金錢，甚至要數以億計。&rdquo;Joe透露《復仇者聯盟3》和《復仇者聯盟4》的拍攝期間，每天大約要耗費45萬美元以上才能保持電影的正常拍攝進度。"},{"pid":"a393b631be1d62fedb3c5a91e5c28b1bedd380e4","tid":656970,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T16:50:45.000Z","msg":"Joseph Russo知道哭是沒有用的"},{"pid":"c5882e515dcd4caecabcec7756bf772ba486edaf","tid":656970,"uid":160551,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T16:51:32.000Z","msg":"怕咩，賺得番<br />\n一日既票房除番開都賺多幾倍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3206b2e70111770c65c2d33f8daa4456b7652614","tid":656970,"uid":169392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T16:52:38.000Z","msg":"票房保證 啲錢點燒都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7810bb3211fb03afd6eeafd9f9cb4a7bb40e082","tid":656970,"uid"